          x = bicgstab (A, b, [], n)

     EXAMPLE 2: ‘bicgstab’ with a function which computes ‘A * X’

          x = bicgstab (Afcn, b, [], n)

     EXAMPLE 3: ‘bicgstab’ with a preconditioner matrix M

          x = bicgstab (A, b, [], 1e-06, n, M)

