     [1] Y. Saad.  "Preconditioning Techniques."  ‘Iterative Methods for Sparse Linear Systems’, PWS Publishing Company, 1996.

     [2] M. Jones, P. Plassmann: ‘An Improved Incomplete Cholesky Factorization’, 1992.

